            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": null,
              "free_text": [
                "The contribution  of  partial  reaction (g,3n)  cross",
                " section  into  the  experimental total neutron yield",
                " reaction  (g,xn)  cross   section   obtained   using",
                " quasimonoenergetic annihilation photons at Livermore",
                " (USA) was  evaluated  using  specially theoretically",
                " calculated transitional  multiplicity   function   -",
                " ratio",
                "     F3-theor = SIG-theor(g,3n)/SIG-theor(g,xn)",
                " by the way",
                "     SIG-eval(g,3n) = (F2-theor)x(SIG-exp(g,xn))."
              ]
